   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_3_00004"/>Dr. <hi rend="latintype">Arthur <damage agent="water"><unclear>Schnitz</unclear></damage>ler</hi>, <rs ref="#pmb168934" type="place">Wien IX.
                  Frankga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e 1</rs>.</addrLine></address><address><addrLine><pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_3_00003"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb34860" type="place">Steindorf</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">am <rs ref="#pmb40374" type="place">Ossiacher</rs>-See</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb651" type="place">Kärnthen</rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_3_00005"/><rs ref="#pmb860" type="place">Graz</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date when="1898-07-15">15/7 98</date></dateline></opener><p><salute>Mein lieber Richard,</salute><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag den 17.</date> verla<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e ich <rs ref="#pmb860" type="place">Graz</rs>, komme auf mancherlei Art am <date>21.</date>
               nach <rs ref="#pmb34014" type="place"><hi rend="latintype"><hi rend="underline" n="1">Bad Gastein, Villa Wassing</hi></hi></rs>, zu meiner <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12701" subtype="implied">Mama</rs>, wo
               ich bis <date>23.</date> bleibe und ein Wort von Ihnen erwarte. Radle dann nach <rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Salzburg</rs>, bin<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>päte<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tens <date>Din<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag 26.</date>
               dort und bleibe bis <date>28</date>; radle da<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> (in
               Ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ell<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chaft) <pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_3_00006"/>nach <rs ref="#pmb39752" type="place">Tegern<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ee</rs>. <rs ref="#pmb11740" type="person">Hugo</rs> hat Ihnen ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chrieben
               – werden wir uns al<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o am <date>9. Augu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t</date> circa irgendwo treffen, um <subst><del rend="overwritten"><unclear>b</unclear></del><add place="inline">a</add></subst>uf 10 Tage minde<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tens zu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>a<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en zu bleiben? Machen
               Sie’s doch möglich. Können Sie zwi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chen <date>23</date> u <date>26. d.</date> nach
                  <rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Salzburg</rs> kommen? – Arbeiten Sie was?</p><p>Grüßen Sie <rs ref="#pmb10860" type="person">Paula</rs> und <rs ref="#pmb2668" type="person">Mirjam</rs>.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
